data-triple-N3.o: "Pitchfork Media, usually known simply as Pitchfork, is a Chicago-based daily Internet publication devoted to music criticism and commentary, music news, and artist interview. Its focus is on independent music, especially indie rock. However, the range of musical genres covered extends to pop, hip-hop, folk, jazz, metal, experimental, and various forms of electronic."@en
